column2: SELECT TOP # g.objid, g.run, g.rerun, g.camcol, g.field, g.obj, g.ra, g.dec, g.clean, sp.z, sp.zErr, zs.nvote as votes, zs.p_el as elliptical, zs.p_cw as spiralclock, zs.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zs.p_edge as edgeon, zs.p_dk as dontknow, zs.p_mg as merger, zs.p_el_debiased as debiased_elliptical, zs.p_cs_debiased as debiased_spiral, zs.spiral as debiased_spiral_ind, zs.elliptical as debiased_elliptical_ind, zs.uncertain as debiased_uncertain_ind FROM Galaxy as G JOIN ZooSpec AS zs ON G.objid = zs.objid JOIN SpecPhoto as sp ON sp.objID = zs.objid
